<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: functional_specification
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification">
<p>
An <b>functional_specification</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/>  that implements the ARM
concept of  <express_ref linkend="Functional_specification:arm:Functional_specification_arm.Functional_specification"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_specification.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification.wr:WR1">
The <b>functional_specification</b> shall be in exactly one 'functional characteristic category'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_specification.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification.wr:WR2">
The <b>functional_specification</b> shall reference exactly one 'characterizing signal for functional specification'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_specification.WR3
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification.wr:WR3">
The <b>functional_specification</b> shall reference exactly one 'reference signal for functional specification'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_specification.WR4
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification.wr:WR4">
The <b>functional_specification</b> shall be no other type of representation.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_specification.WR5
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification.wr:WR5">
The <b>functional_specification</b> name shall be blank.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_specification.WR6
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification.wr:WR6">
The <b>functional_specification</b> shall reference exactly one  <express_ref linkend="Network_functional_design_view:mim:Network_functional_design_view_mim.component_functional_unit"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: functional_specification_definition
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification_definition">
<p>
A <b>functional_specification_definition</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Network_functional_usage_view:mim:Network_functional_usage_view_mim.functional_unit"/> that implements the ARM concept
of  <express_ref linkend="Functional_specification:arm:Functional_specification_arm.Functional_specification_definition"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_specification_definition.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification_definition.wr:WR1">
The <b>functional_specification_definition</b> context shall be 'functional network design'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_specification_definition.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification_definition.wr:WR2">
The <b>functional_specification_definition</b> shall be related to at least one  <express_ref linkend="Functional_specification:mim:Functional_specification_mim.functional_specification"/>.
</ext_description>

